\begin{verse}
kaM|| aMtado LAdiyakaLiyuta | leMtiha gaCaCxdoLagoMda naLiyutaladariM|| niMtiha sheVSavanahxrisalf | baMtenisuva labadhxvAgalutatxrakeVLeY||

